55618653ecca9c677","tid":209431,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"佢地仲以為長毛同社民連個名好有吸引力？<br />\n莫財cap水都唔好咁蠢"},{"pid":"a56748ecfc54f192ba7b444d3a8cfd2b55aeb693","tid":209431,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n社會民主連線2017抗爭青年實習計劃<br />\n對象：大專生，理念與社民連相近，有志於改變社會<br />\n日期：6月初至8月底<br />\n<br />\n時間：每星期最少兩至三天<br />\n<br />\n學習課題：左翼視野、性別分析、分配公義、福利政策、社運歷史<br />\n<br />\n工作內容：政策研究、小組學習、地區宣傳、組織行動<br />\n<br />\n截止日期：2017年5月20日<br />\n<br />\n（本會將提供微薄的車馬費津貼）"},{"pid":"7899907eafd33555a70d45c68204db98833f9bc1","tid":209431,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:37:11.000Z","msg":"性名分析都要學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc2b598f9cb3db51e91848ecdc58f0f04361fdb","tid":209431,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"教你係行人路開劍圍？"},{"pid":"b695bde7c0c7742bd4e65cb55874ba8fdf0fdac6","tid":209431,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番大陸睇水塘啦<br />\n哲古華拉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哲古華拉T<br />\n<br />\n佢都仲好意思著"},{"pid":"a5268cee0ef5ae0b77e982e52b0565e75df24f67","tid":209431,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學光頭佬cap水？</blockquote><br />\n熱血少年軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6deb4a4c960235c2e4865492f6be841df1839ee","tid":209431,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z0CDWeJiOXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz0CDWeJiOXw&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3a7c25cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z0CDWeJiOXw</a><br />\n聲帶同相都係於今日2014年10月19日約11am影到同錄到<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qJyXcir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqJyXcir.jpg&h=3c6d7cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Hjc5coA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHjc5coA.jpg&h=8fa47f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為不是我親身錄，所以請自行判斷係咪佢！<br />\n<br />\n以下是script:<br />\n0000-0008<br />\n唔能知.....<br />\n唔能知佢係熱血公民&amp;#22021;<br />\n0009-0014<br />\n咁我... 最緊要就...<br />\n總之唔係度&amp;#13774;啦<br />\n呀...哥<br />\n0014-0017<br />\n&hellip;姐呀，我去屈臣氏呀<br />\n0018-0023<br />\n喂？哦，係呀係呀，你&amp;#21946;上便&amp;#21526;，就&amp;#21946;上便等，上便等&amp;#21526;<br />\n0026-0030<br />\n所以班友仔呢，係不....&amp;#22021;<br />\n0031-0037<br />\ner當然我不排除有個別呢&hellip; 即係我都係，我都係見到係&amp;#21946;個，最前線果度&amp;#22021;<br />\n0037-0042<br />\n&hellip;膠棒我一見到佢&amp;#21707;擋果d &hellip; 我&amp;#21707;擋緊佢d遮&amp;#13774;嘛<br />\n0042-0051<br />\n而我睇呢，有d呢，老實講，就係咪佢都已經腎上腺標升<br />\n唔知喎<br />\n冇人知喎<br />\n0051-0054<br />\n因為我見... 拎返尋日.....<br />\n5400-5800<br />\n我，我其實都帶&amp;#21655;兩隻色&amp;#22175;&amp;#13774;啦<br />\n你嗌...彎通<br />\n5900-0103<br />\n你&amp;#21707;細...學教室呀？唔好落，唔好落...<br />\n我&amp;#21707;不嬲d..<br />\n0103-0110<br />\n第二樣&amp;#22050;就係，如果，其實現場情形的話呢，你用... &amp;#25886;到&amp;#22021;<br />\n0110-0116<br />\n&hellip;多謝你&amp;#21707;啦 ，即係話，幫手....<br />\n老實講&amp;#21526;...<br />\n希望大家都出d力啦<br />\n0116-0119<br />\n最大&amp;#22021;...度...<br />\n咁陳國治呢？<br />\n畀人..&amp;#21655;<br />\n0119-0127<br />\n我諗掉返轉頭，政治上最難收拾&amp;#22021;，我&amp;#21707;只係最不容易放&amp;#13774;&amp;#21867;<br />\n&amp;#22001;當然... &amp;#22175;睇呢<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"7dd90a16dc9340ab252a07a48b41a4d58dfb6d34","tid":209431,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"睇返wiki, 大將軍從政之前個cv都幾勁<br />\n點解仲撈政治<img src=\"/assets/